<BODY>Dear colleagues! <BR><BR>Every year we recognize our best colleagues and teams for their outstanding contribution to the business and nominate them for The Best in Tallink awards. It is time to do it again! To find out, who are our most professional employees, our supportive and helpful colleagues, and co-workers, who are most appreciated by our customers, it is important that all of us contribute to the nomination process and submit our colleagues for the awards. <BR><BR>Awards are given out in 18 different catergories. Let us know, who deserves special gratitude and recognition this year! Click on the link to open the submission form: https://tallink.eu.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_djr4tOnlxf4O6Oh. The submission form is open until 18 December 2019. <BR><BR>Awards will be handed over at the annual Tallink Grupp Awards Gala held on 7 February 2020 at Alexela Concert Hall in Tallinn. <BR><BR>More information in Insider and from HR and Development Director Vahur Ausmees, vahur.ausmees@tallink.ee or +3725055002. <BR><BR></BODY></html>

